        'Order of operations daily warm-up — build from simple to complex with brackets and braces',
        'Fraction unit review with fraction bars and number lines — do NOT skip even for borderline students',
        'Error-analysis routine: students justify WHY an answer is wrong using math vocabulary',
        'Decimal place value visualization: meter sticks, decimal grids, money',
        'iReady: maintain 45+ min/week; use teacher dashboard to monitor lesson completion',
        'Growth goal conferences: review % progress to typical growth target weekly',
