        'MA.5.M, MA.5.DP — Conversions, volume, line plots with fractions',
        'MA.5.GR.1–4 — 2D classification hierarchies, coordinate plane, composite figures'
      ],
      strategies: [
        'Whole-class rigorous Tier 1 instruction with differentiated questioning and tiered tasks',
